{
  "stem": "107.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was really the worst transportation that I ever had to experience.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And finally, we come to a place where the train stopped-- a small train station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I look out the window.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was this one little window like in cattle cars, where you had to step on somebody else, or somebody had to help you up to look out, and I see the word Osviecim-- Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now I remember the letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I know I had only one thought and said it to my former secretary-- the woman that I had mentioned, who also was in the transport-- if they only would give us something to drink before they kill us.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, that was my last wish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I said it, of course, in a kind of half jokingly-- seriously joking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she obviously loved me, because she had volunteered to go in the transport when she couldn't take me out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was sorry that I was not, because I know that she was devoted as a person only can be.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She wrote a whole book for me that I had read during this time, and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was willing to-- I mean, she would have sooner or later gone there anyway, but wanted to be there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe to please herself to be with me, help me, if it's possible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was a very-- this woman was married to a Czech pilot, who was in the American-- no, in the Czech air force, prior to the invasion of the Germans, and flew with his airplane to England and became a part of the Czech squadron of [INAUDIBLE] pilots.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They opened the-- the cars, and the famous screaming starts, out, out, out!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fast!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Run!",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
